                <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl">webpack-compiler-csharp-net-core</h1>
                <p class="mt-6 text-xl">🔧 A boilerplate project demonstrating how to integrate Webpack with ASP.NET Core (.NET 8) using modern JavaScript tooling powered by pnpm.</p>

                <h2 class="mt-10 text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900">🚀 Features</h2>
                <ul class="mt-4 list-disc list-inside">
                    <li>Webpack + ASP.NET Core (.NET 8)</li>
                    <li>Hot Module Replacement (HMR)</li>
                    <li>Production & development builds</li>
                    <li>Modern JS tooling via pnpm</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="mt-10 text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900">📦 Prerequisites</h2>
                <p class="mt-2">Ensure you have these installed:</p>
                <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside">
                    <li>.NET 8 SDK</li>
                    <li>Node.js (LTS)</li>
                    <li>pnpm</li>
                    <li>Visual Studio 2022 or VS Code</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-4">Install pnpm globally (if needed):</p>
                <pre class="bg-gray-100 p-2 rounded text-sm text-indigo-600"><code>npm install -g pnpm</code></pre>

                <h2 class="mt-10 text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900">🛠️ Installation</h2>
                <p class="mt-2">Clone the Repository:</p>
                <pre class="bg-gray-100 p-2 rounded text-sm text-indigo-600"><code>git clone https://github.com/TysonGerber/webpack-compiler-csharp-net-core.git
cd webpack-compiler-csharp-net-core</code></pre>
                <p class="mt-4">Restore .NET Dependencies:</p>
                <pre class="bg-gray-100 p-2 rounded text-sm text-indigo-600"><code>dotnet restore</code></pre>
                <p class="mt-4">Install JavaScript Dependencies with pnpm:</p>
                <pre class="bg-gray-100 p-2 rounded text-sm text-indigo-600"><code>cd webpackFinishedBoilerPlate
pnpm install</code></pre>

                <h2 class="mt-10 text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900">🔧 Development Workflow</h2>
                <p class="mt-2 font-semibold">1. Start Webpack Dev Server (with HMR):</p>
                <pre class="bg-gray-100 p-2 rounded text-sm text-indigo-600"><code>pnpm start</code></pre>
                <p class="mt-4 font-semibold">2. Run the ASP.NET Core Backend:</p>
                <pre class="bg-gray-100 p-2 rounded text-sm text-indigo-600"><code>dotnet run</code></pre>
                <p class="mt-2">Then visit: <a href="https://localhost:5001" class="text-blue-500 underline">https://localhost:5001</a></p>

                <h2 class="mt-10 text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900">🏗️ Build for Production</h2>
                <p class="mt-2 font-semibold">Bundle frontend assets:</p>
                <pre class="bg-gray-100 p-2 rounded text-sm text-indigo-600"><code>pnpm build</code></pre>
                <p class="mt-4 font-semibold">Publish .NET App:</p>
                <pre class="bg-gray-100 p-2 rounded text-sm text-indigo-600"><code>dotnet publish -c Release</code></pre>
                <p class="mt-2">This creates a production-ready version of your site in the <code>publish/</code> directory.</p>

